{"tid":9584,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得自己有朋友同冇朋友冇分別?","createTime":"2016-11-28T15:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T00:37:57.000Z","uid":22505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"399005473c711e776b5244a32e464c5ea7cf7e51","tid":9584,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:48:29.000Z","msg":"朋友已經好少剩返個d又好似唔係朋友咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有個雖然識左7年又成日都一齊出街食飯<br />\n但事實上出到街大家有自己食好少話題傾<br />\n就而行去搭/坐地鐵成條路都可以冇開過聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nwhatsapp又係已讀不回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一個朋友又係識左7年<br />\n大家有時都會係whatsapp 講下心事<br />\n其實我已經當左佢係交心朋友<br />\n有一次同第二個朋友鬧交仲反埋面<br />\n估唔到佢唔會幫我講說話仲係到食花生<br />\n我真係對佢好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外個班就有兩個朋友識左3年<br />\n雖然出到街大家有好多話題傾<br />\n但一返到屋企佢地唔會同你whatsapp<br />\n試過做主動whatsapp佢地<br />\n點知佢地兩個都係已讀不回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時無聊想揾佢地傾下計都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解我d朋友一個二個都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a708e70eacd3057f457cf7ac250cabb539743ed","tid":9584,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:54:11.000Z","msg":"咁如果冇朋友你又有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講真又幾自由自在"},{"pid":"97f381632b7b25e5bc4e0df8362709e3512514c4","tid":9584,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:06:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁如果冇朋友你又有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講真又幾自由自在</blockquote><br />\n係幾自由但有時真係好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c963a44953cc60f0910589bc22b26ab68e86e55","tid":9584,"uid":9271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:06:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁如果冇朋友你又有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講真又幾自由自在</blockquote><br />\n係幾自由但有時真係好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n行街見到一班人<br />\n而你只有一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a171e9fd6175f40f623d1cd9bbd1c4429a690c","tid":9584,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:40:31.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n回覆左冇提示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲以為樓主唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49585326f2ccc4c511bfdaaba4e641c514a9ffa9","tid":9584,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:14:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;咁如果冇朋友你又有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講真又幾自由自在</blockquote><br />\n係幾自由但有時真係好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n行街見到一班人<br />\n而你只有一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我反而好憎見到人地一大班人<br />\n我覺得佢地好撚嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d1fe6e2a7938ff6bd25843eaf884cdbf70af8e","tid":9584,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:15:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌<br />\n回覆左冇提示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲以為樓主唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n慘得過我次次開post都咁少咁回<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f852ea0144b81be0d06bc694e01a47411b065591","tid":9584,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:16:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"328803795036d3a740