/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"498effd59127800d749c11850614128e21c4b895","tid":9584,"uid":8930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T00:30:34.000Z","msg":"樣子問題吧。<br />\n我亦如是<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82c76aa92c575f718beb3bfa4e277429c237f15","tid":9584,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T00:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樣子問題吧。<br />\n我亦如是<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  見你樣衰真係唔想同你行埋一齊"},{"pid":"a28f565593bd9fdd3cf9d4502cfc806a7ddea67f","tid":9584,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T00:37:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樣子問題吧。<br />\n我亦如是<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  見你樣衰真係唔想同你行埋一齊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n利申試過比人咁對待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}